social_posts.post_text: Celebrate Seven Days of Aloha with us! Every day for the next 7 days we will be featuring selected items for sale at 50% off (with no code needed). Day 1 features select styles of our popular Fringe Hoop Earrings. Link in bio to shop #SevenDaysofAloha

Day 2 of our Seven Days of Aloha!  For today, get 50% off our Interlocking Branches Necklace (with no code needed). Cast from real branches found in the forest, this necklace features two joined circles in a timeless symbol meaning “together forever”. Each individual circle is designed with delicate buds showing the promise of new growth. Perfect for mothers and daughters, best friends, and significant others. Link in bio to shop #Seven Days of Aloha

Day 3 of our Seven Days of Aloha!  Capture the magic of stars with today’s variety: get 50% off our beautifully textured Koa Star Posts and our unique Star Shaker Necklaces which includes crystals or birthstones.  Link in bio to shop #Seven Days of Aloha

Day 4 of our Seven Days of Aloha! Today’s selections are from two classic collections, our Shakers and our Botanicals all in classic hues of blue. (50% off without a code). Link in bio to shop #SevenDaysofAloha

Day 5 of our Seven Days of Aloha features a number of elegant pieces from our Sealife collection.  Now is your chance to pick up a variety of starfish, sharks, and turtles inspired by the sea creatures that make Hawaii’s waters their own.  Link in bio to shop #SevenDaysofAloha

Day 6 of our Seven Days of Aloha!  All 3 styles of our signature Coral Rings (Thin, Wide, and Extra Wide) are 50% off today (without a code). Cast from real fan coral found on the beaches of Hawaii, these gorgeous gifts from the ocean offer organic and unusual patterns and textures that can be worn every day.  Follow the link in our bio to shop #SevenDaysofAloha

Day 7 of our Seven Days of Aloha!  Inspired by the endearing beauty of the Hawaiian seashore, our Opihi circles add a simple statement with a lasting impression. The natural texture of the opihi shell adds a sophisticated edge blended with just the right amount of glamour. Link in our bio to shop #SevenDaysofAloha

Introducing the Lineage collection!⁠
⁠
This collection is entirely customized based on you! What does that mean?⁠
⁠
Did you know that each month is affiliated with a flower? We created this collection specifically for Mother’s Day with the idea of creating a birth flower “bouquet” that represents up to 4 individuals. Whether it’s immediate family, friends, generations of women in your family, or something else entirely, this custom piece will not only be beautiful, but will be unique to you.

Photos @planit_marketing

The recent devastation on the Island of Maui has hit very close to home for us.  One of our artisans is a native of Maui, born and raised. We all have friends, family, and colleagues who are directly affected by this tragedy.  The news and photos have been unbelievable, unfathomable, and unreal for us all. 

As a local company, we are committed to our community by helping in any way we can. 

Starting today, 8/10 (until next Friday, 8/18) Catherine Weitzman Jewelry will be donating 100% of online sales on catherineweitzman.com towards The American Red Cross for disaster relief and recovery on Maui.

We are one ‘ohana.  Please consider directly donating and reaching out to @hawaiiredcross, @mauiunitedway, @hawaiicommunityfoundation and/or the @salarmyhi.

In the wake of the devastation in Lāhainā, we have teamed up with Good Morning America and other brands to help raise funds for the people of Maui. Our customers’ generosity has already been tremendous, but we’d love to amplify that momentum in order  to further assist  devastated local people in the wake of this tragedy. You can help us raise funds by shopping Catherine Weitzman on Good Morning America's Deals and Steals @gmadeals .The proceeds will all go to the ongoing disaster relief and recovery efforts in the Island of Maui. For a limited time, you can receive up to 70% off our birthstone and botanical collection. If your selection is sold out, DM us and we’ll try our best to help you find the perfect item. Mahalo to everyone who has generously supported already!
